The Main Squeeze

Category(s):
FOOD TRUCKS & VENDORS
Welcome to The Main Squeeze of North Florida. We make fresh, homemade, specialty lemonades. We service Clay, Duval, Nassau and St. Johns counties. We are available for birthday parties, weddings, showers, craft markets and festivals. Please contact us for your next event or get-together!
